{"type": "article", "id": 3348, "title": "羊毛拖鞋", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-07T07:56:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232639JGZw7Bk1EzoXVfMA.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t2010 年，Gaspard Tiné-Berès 前往伦敦皇家艺术学院学习，在寒冷的冬天赤脚在家行走时，他突发奇想剪下了一块毛料，拿运动鞋鞋带进行简单缝制后便成了一双简易拖鞋，且穿起来非常保暖舒适。于是，他决定设计一款拖鞋，采用法国羊毛材质作为鞋面，皮革材质作为鞋底，并给拖鞋配上了颜色明亮的鞋带，在 2013 时上线 Kickstarter 进行众筹。如今，这款名为「Lasso」的拖鞋已正式面世，提供蓝、绿、橙 3 色鞋带可选，定价 49 美元，<a href=\"http://store.hypebeast.com/brands/lasso/orange-lasso-slippers\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232636FyWfrTgmL1Nk0sUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232636V3wF4TODY6b8Bv9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232637W1iAhDXRPvEG7rno.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232637gQE7PJqzt83YGbf6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232638ZJ6QrXmeMcuAf8kC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}